    "name": "Contractors and supervisors, other construction trades, installers, repairers and servicers",
    "lead statement": "This unit group includes roofing, masonry, painting and other construction trade contractors, not elsewhere classified, who own and operate their business. Supervisors in this unit group supervise and co-ordinate the activities of various tradespersons, installers, repairers and servicers classified in the following minor groups:  (728),  (729) and  (744). They are employed by a wide range of establishments; places of employment are indicated in the unit group descriptions. This unit group also includes prefabricated product installation and service contractors and proprietors of some repair and service establishments.",
